{"tid":1009320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝團年飲茶真係好尷尬！","createTime":"2019-02-05T05:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T06:20:06.000Z","uid":80999,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f63b95067a7ce029234fdf1a15bc1d92edf35c2","tid":1009320,"uid":80999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"話說每年年初一我阿媽嗰邊都會飲個早茶<br />\n今年都唔例外<br />\n<br />\n不過我大姨媽同二姨媽不嬲都水火不容<br />\n(事源係一齊買股票有爭執)<br />\n<br />\n食左一半兩條友開始黎料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大姨媽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二姨媽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 恭喜你個仔今年娶老婆喎 真係娶得嬌妻呀(個嬌特別大聲) 黎黎黎食條菜 綠色啱你個仔呀 (大表哥個老婆以前係lkf蒲開嗰d)<br />\n<br />\n二姨媽聽完黑晒面 <br />\n<br />\n過左陣其他親戚係度傾緊隔離雜貨舖有d西(隔水嗰隻) 話好好用 推薦大家去買<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 隔離都無黑色 都係betty姐(大姨媽) 屋企嗰個好用 黑色既幾好睇<br />\n<br />\n我阿婆老到有d懵 完全唔知佢地係有野 仲懵盛盛話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : (認真mode) 唉也 個西用左咁多年一定變黑啦 得閒換過個啦"},{"pid":"54a0ff54c707fc56d923c2a03d245aa8804d3627","tid":1009320,"uid":15483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbf3268cd2b02bba853bc68fc8ea45f2d0af280","tid":1009320,"uid":80999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54a0ff54c707fc56d923c2a03d245aa8804d3627","tid":1009320,"uid":15483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" cl